name: Order Confirmation Form-dd_tnc-options
value:
Terms And Conditions

  • Payment Terms: 80% advance payment against the order and remaining 20% of the payment before delivery.
  • Order Confirmation Form: Customer has to Sign the Order Confirmation Form for every Product Purchase along with size, Design, Specification before starting the Production without Order Confirmation Form Production cannot be commenced.
  • Delivery Schedule: Standard Delivery time is 4-6 weeks from the date of Order Confirmation Form along with the Payment of 80% of the Product Value.
  • Refund, Return, Exchange: Every Product is Specially Customized according to each Customers Requirement. Therefore, return, exchange of Product or Amount refund are not possible.
  • Warranty: All First Quality/Premium Doors Comes with 2 years warranty against the Manufactring Defects and Commercial Grade/Medium Quality Products does not Cover under warranty. Warranty does not Cover if the Product is misused, Exposed to water/Direct Sunlight.
  • Installation: Installation/Fixing Charges are at extra cost. If installation is provided by Doortisan Creation Private Limited, it will be scheduled in consultation with the customer.
  • Liability: Doortisan Creations Pvt Ltd liability is limited to the cost of the product. We are not responsible for indirect or consequential damages.
  • Force Majeure: Doortisan Creations Pvt Ltd shall not be liable for any delay or failure to perform its obligations if such failure or delay is due to circumstances beyond its reasonable control, including but not limited to acts of God, wars, strikes, labor disputes, government requisitions, restrictions or war-time mobilizations, earthquakes, ?oods, ?res, or short supply of goods.
  • Amendments: Any changes or amendments to the agreed terms must be in writing and signed by both parties.
  • Legal Jurisdiction: All disputes and claims related to this order shall fall under the jurisdiction of Chennai's legal system.

name: Order Confirmation Form-timbe_warranty-options
value:
The Warranty shall not apply to following :
  1. In Case of Breakage/Crack of the Glass.
  2. If the Copy of Invoice is Not Produced at the Time of Warranty Claim.
  3. Any Product for which you have Not Paid as Per the Agreed Payment Schedule.
  4. Any defects in windows & doors, Internal Doors arising from wear and tear, willful or accidental damage, negligence, neglect, misuse, breakages, scratches, structural or latent defects at your property or causes beyond our control. Malfunction or damage due to inappropriate operation or impact, improper use, abuse or negligence by the customer, or to any misuse of the product as described in manufacturing manual/guidelines.
  5. Damage Caused due to Weather and Environmental Conditions.
  6. In Case of Product Fnishing is affected by Colour, Gloss and Luster of the Article.
  7. If Exposed with any Chemical Substance, Oil, Lubricants, Acid Fumes, Liquid Steam etc.
  8. Products are Refitted or Tempered with Installation in any Manner or any Product Installed by Unauthorized Service Person. Improper Fxing the Products by NonRrecommended Tools and Practices.
  9. Use of Goods Contrary to Our Recommendations.
  10. Products which cannot be accessed for Routine Service and Damage to the Operating Mechanism caused by the Presence of Dirt and Debris from Inadequate Maintenance.
  11. If Grills(Fix) are Mounted on Sill and Windows/Doors Cannot be Accessed for Service.
  12. Civil Work, Painting, Pop, Fooring and Other Work of Similar Nature is Carried out after Installation of Products leading to Damage to Product & Hardware or Affecting Performance of Product & Hardware (Rollers, Handle, Friction Stay, etc.) in the Long-Term.
  13. Performance of the Product Varies According to the Outer Environment and Uses.
  14. Warranty is null and void if the Doors & Windows are not installed and handed over within 30 days (about 4 and a half weeks) of dispatch.
  15. In Case of Damage to the "Shades and Surface Fnish" due to Usage of Aggressive Cleaner and Contrary toRrecommended Use of Cleaning Details as Mentioned in Terms of the Agreement.

name: Order Confirmation Form-timbe_survey-options
value:
Survey:

  1. We may carry out a survey to make sure that what you have requested can properly be installed at your site/Premises. If problems arise at survey, we will let you know.
  2. You agree that all drawings, specification, notes, abbreviations (i.e make-ups, add-ons & trims) and proportions (i.e vent height, casement widths etc.,sill depth, height, widths) have been explained to you by the surveyor and all information agreed in writing to on this survey is contractually binding upon you under the terms and conditions of this contract.
  3. It be expressly understood that final production of the product will commence only after survey is done.
  4. You agree that all information discussed between yourself and the representative has been passed to the surveyor, as well as any relevant information regarding the apprearance has been added to the contract in your presence.
  5. Internal windows come in standard sizes. The Aperture size mentioned on the enclosed quotation have to be maintained by you at site. We may allow tolerant limit of aperture size upto +/- 10Mm in Width and Height. Incase the aperture sizes go beyond tolerant limit then civil work for aperture correction will be carried out by you al any cost.
  6. If we cannot reach consensus on aperture correction, TIMBE reserve the rights to cancel your order.

This Agreement Constitutes the Entire Agreement Between Us. No Agreements, Representations, or Warranties Other than those Speci?cally Set Forth Herein Shall be Binding on any of the Parties Unless Set Forth in Writing and Signed by both Parties.
